sx.blah.discord.util.audio.providers

Class GlobalProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • sx.blah.discord.util.audio.providers.GlobalProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAudioProvider

    public class GlobalProvider
extends Object
implements IAudioProvider
    GlobalProvider allows for an IAudioProvider to provide the same audio across multiple IAudioManager instances.
